ning</strong><span> is my favorite concept in business strategy.&nbsp;</spa=
n></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margi=
n: 0 0 20px 0;"><span>Hamilton Helmer, who includes counter-positioning as =
