elative;"><strong>The Downside of Being Positioned</strong></h3><p style=3D=
"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;"><=
span>When OpenAI launched ChatGPT late last year, Google was caught predict=
ably flat-footed. Less than a month after ChatGPT&#8217;s launch, Google CE=
O Sundar Pichai </span><a href=3D"https://substack.com/redirect/c62e909b-f2=
ac-46ad-804e-c7c45f731386?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlXXepK=
