;"><span>As I highlighted in </span><em><a href=3D"https://substack.com/red=
irect/9c16e2c8-3bad-4fb2-936c-83ac68f39b85?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7Gn=
