 text-decoration: underline;">Why Did I Leave Google, Or Why Did I Stay So =
Long?</a></em><span> Bardin paints a picture of a company more focused on p=
rotecting itself than serving its users. This post is worth a read too, but=
 his conclusion makes the point succinctly: </span><strong>&#8220;The innov=
ation challenges at Corp-Tech will only get worse as the risk tolerance wil=
l go down. Soon, Lawyers &gt; Builders and the builders will need to go els=
